name: Hellowicked 03: Skeleton In My Closet
description:
"I spit on behalf of my death cult made of millions of morbid angels/ Standing in a burning church in Norway lost in hatred/ Of course Satan smiles through the face of a child/ Whose born with the number of the Devil scraped into his scalp" - Ill Bill, "Black Metal"

My album is straight up Helloween. The OG on the cover of the "Swagton Nirojim" is pure blackness. In the true spirit of elitist underground black metal, this will be a limited edition drop. - Krowbar

The third in a series of NFTs until October 31st. Burn everything left after 24 hours.
